Citigroup’s Asia Pacific Islamic Head Amray Joins Al Rajhi Bank

-- B y   K h a l i d   Q a y u m
-- 
2011-03-01T04:28:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/citigroup-s-asia-pacific-islamic-head-amray-joins-al-rajhi-bank.html
Mudassir Amray joined  Saudi Arabia ’s  Al Rajhi Bank  in  Malaysia  today after resigning as head of Asia
Pacific Islamic banking at  Citigroup Inc . He was based in  Singapore  for the past few months and prior to that  Hong Kong .  Amray’s new post is the head of wholesale banking at the
Kingdom’s largest publicly traded lender, he said in a phone
interview from  Kuala Lumpur  where he’s now based.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Khalid Qayum in Singapore 
 kqayum@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sandy Hendry at 
 shendry@bloomberg.net . 